---
title: get_data_column_sidecars_from_block (fulu-validator)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init : start
    q_init --> q_extract : blob_kzg_commitments = signed_block.message.body.blob_kzg_commitments
    q_extract --> q_header : signed_block_header = compute_signed_block_header(signed_block)
    q_header --> q_proof : kzg_commitments_inclusion_proof = compute_merkle_proof(body, generalized_index)
    q_proof --> [*] : return get_data_column_sidecars(header, commitments, proof, cells_and_kzg_proofs)

    note right of q_header
        INV: signed_block must be a valid SignedBeaconBlock
        INV: Merkle proof is computed over blob_kzg_commitments field in block body
        INV: Delegates to get_data_column_sidecars with extracted components
    end note
